review: Dr. Pranshu was very skilled at his work. He explained the condition and treatment plan very well. To top it all he's kind and respectful of all patients. My husband also sought treatment from him.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: It was my pleasure to visit Dr. Pranshu. He is a true gentleman and professional. I live in Toronto and was not satisfied with the services and attention given by local doctors there. I saw JR Dental clinic reviews online and immediately connected to Dr. Pranshu, who is very friendly and knowledgable in his field. It felt like I am talking to my best friend. He not only gave me correct advice, but also helped me understand the problem well and designed a future roadmap/action plan by which I can have excellent dental health. I flew down to Dwarka, New Delhi especially to get treated by him. I would strongly recommend JR Dental clinic, Dr. Avantika and Dr. Pranshu.. for patient not only in india, however outside india and living in abroad. Prices are very economical and treatment is very trustworthy. Thank you Doctor for having me here.

I got my RCT and crown from Dr. Pranshu Tripathi, the treatment was painless. I am very happy by the outcome. Before treatment I was in a lot of pain, was not able to eat and sleep. My pain was relieved and I was almost normal within one day.
Thank you so much Dr Pranshu and JR Dental team.

Dr Priyanshu is the one of the most  trustable dentists i have ever come across. He is very humble and grounded doctor. He said mine was the longest running root canal, because i could not come to clinc on the set days, but was always kind in talking and humble. He is very polite. I am gald that i went to him and nowhere else. Most importantly he is one doctor  who would never ask for any extra penne.

I had rescheduled appointment with Dr. Pranshu Tripathi for my mother and we have visited clinic. Doctor was **** *** professional with us, ** *** ****** ***** *********. He had done the complete check up and explained all the things in detail for us, we are completely satisfied with this doctor and I would like to highly recommend for him. In clinic all the things was fine like no waiting time, positive staff response, hygienic clinic all others also.

Great service, friendly Doctor. I got my RCT done from Dr. Pranshu Tripathi and I am quite satisfied with the treatment. Highly recommended. I'am glad that I chose his paid service. Thank you Dr. Pranshu for the painless treatment and your kind support.

Awesome Doctor!

review: I visited Dr.Pranshu Tripathi for Root canal treatment. Doctor was really friendly, polite and gave a detailed explanation of the intensity of the issue. Satisfied with the treatment and recommend the doctor to others as well!
Very friendly and punctual. Very clean work....RCT done very smoothly without any pain. Will surely recommend for any teeth related issues
I had a great experience with Dr. Pranshu. My Root canal treatment went smoothly with him. I would highly recommend him.

review:

One sitting and I felt good improvement. Strongly recommended.
